Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}醫師 小池醫師!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有哪裡不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}步未...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我妹妹呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}很遺憾地 她去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是刑警 染田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}發生這種事 我發自內心地感到遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對於這次的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們一定將全力偵辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}查明真相...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然事情發生地這麼突然 你一定很難接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但就算是為了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你也必須走出來 繼續向前邁進才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}世上有很多事是可以靠時間去沖淡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然也有些事沒辦法啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哪怕只有一點點也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的有報答她什麼過嗎...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我根本完全沒報答過她...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒想到妳竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這麼快就離我而去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算想報答妳...也已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒辦法了啊...
Comment: 0,0:02:06.73,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有什麼吃的嗎...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.52,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}SBM48的那幾位啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那不是「勝利的方程式」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.40,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說他們根本沒有48個人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.57,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是才4個人而已嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.82,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且他們也不是偶像團體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.66,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}其他還有啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.62,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}暑期補習 熱烈報名中...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.83,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼 接著看下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.12,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}金先生拉麵...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.50,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}柚子胡椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.25,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}欸!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.75,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.79,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}順帶一提 這題完整的問題如下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:34.17,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}「聽說金先生拉麵加入某種調味料會變得非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.30,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請問是加什麼調味料呢?」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乙坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乙坂同學 如果還沒吃飯的話 要不要一起吃呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你看 我做了奶油燉菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是柚{\ fn AR P丸ゴシック体E \fs 57.5}咲咲{\ fn 華康華綜體W5 \fs 63}特製的奶油燉菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}才不需要啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...要怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}很遺憾地 他好像又走回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算傾家蕩產也想吃到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}柚{\ fn AR P丸ゴシック体E \fs 57.5}咲咲{\ fn 華康華綜體W5 \fs 63}特製的奶油燉菜啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}少噁心了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這種東西 你要多少就讓柚{\ fn AR P丸ゴシック体E \fs 57.5}咲{\ fn 華康華綜體W5 \fs 63}做多少給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用你的能力 把這門給我撞爛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果是強化玻璃的話還行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但這個門是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為了安全起見 這門做得比一般公寓的門還要堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呿 真是個沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算燒了也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}平時的品味完全湧不上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}失去手足的痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我還以為自己會比一般人要來得能理解的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦? 那個...結果到底怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}或許還需要一點時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我們下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不好意思 我要直接進門囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...我是白柳...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}他還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 應該還好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那接下來就拜託妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是之前被你救過一命的白柳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊...然後咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}聽說你一直都沒去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令妹的事...真的是非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然我也沒立場說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但如果有什麼事是我能幫上忙的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.11,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乙坂同學 我想幫上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幫我的忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我健康~得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哪裡健康啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你一直都只吃泡麵而已吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我喜歡 有什麼不可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...那 之前我們兩個一起去吃過的鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再一起去吃一次吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}鬆餅?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我哪時跟妳去吃過了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是被你救了的那天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}泡麵和鬆餅 營養價值上來說不都差不多嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是沒錯啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 總之 先到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那能拜託妳幫我買箱泡麵回來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳不是要幫我跑腿嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}泡麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哪種都行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不不 乙坂同學你也要和我一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}錢之後會付給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果不是和你一起的話 我就不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼如果不是和我一起的話就不去...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳叫白柳來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳是我的監護人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不...我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 我也用我方式在為你著想著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳不是來跑腿的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對於現在的乙坂同學來說 出門走走是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一直關在家裡的話 心理上會生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心理生病?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我不是說了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我健康得很
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}健康的人才不會過這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這就是你心理生病的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別自作主張地...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把人當作病人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果妳不是來跑腿的 能請妳回去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我多管閒事了 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}得出去買點東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}終於要來硬的了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}白柳搞不好也是因為被人拜託才演那場戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也就是說 我也差不多該出去露個臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我出去一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有這麼多的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}暫時不回宿舍也夠生活了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為了不被那個溼答答的男人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}逃到遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}應該已經夠遠了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}麵吃膩了...吃披薩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒想到我竟然還沒被找到啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是您點的披薩和沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沙拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是另外送的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明不需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天幾號了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}都過這麼久了還沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}應該不會被找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}稍微出去外面看看吧
Comment: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<CM>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請給我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好久沒吃甜食了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有那種遊戲喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這真好玩...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}殺光你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們是要玩到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}差不多該滾蛋了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊? 你是怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}想打架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這傢伙叫我們滾蛋 還把垃圾踢過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘿...你算哪根蔥?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}善良的一般市民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}善良的一般市民會把垃圾踢過來嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}生氣起來的話會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你開什麼玩笑!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}帶他到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是你先找碴的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}稍微讓你吃點苦頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘿...你們贏得了我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要讓你好一段時間沒辦法打電動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你他媽在搞什麼啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}欸!? 我應該在打這傢伙才對啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哎呀 突然在搞內鬨嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒問題吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好痛...什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到底發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有一根哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}住...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不好意思 我太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}下次再來找我麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我就真的殺了你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喲 就是你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一個人幹掉權堂他們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}權堂?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}他們之中好像有這麼一個人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是細山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}給我記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}聽起來就像是個幾分鐘後就會忘記的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好大的膽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們還真是完全被看扁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們稍微教育他一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們在搞什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}先弄瞎你一隻眼睛好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到時候你就會有個「獨眼的細」之類的中二稱號囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你在猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}獨眼...聽起來很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要上囉~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是我輸了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個細山田哥竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的假的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒有人贏得了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比起遊戲 現實要有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是很重要的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...妳是從什麼時候開始...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}從最一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}「最一開始」是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}該不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你就再也沒辦法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}所以我阻止了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是誰要妳這麼做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 我申請休學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是我自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為我覺得 我也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我一直在想 那時候我的判斷是否正確
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是否應該要馬上將小步未保護在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}所以 我會陪你到你振作起來為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我已經這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳少多管閒事!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}剛才也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你想變成廢人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不想做人了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那...妳要我怎麼辦啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯...總之 先好好吃一頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}健康的飲食是活力的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我有好好地在吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只吃披薩和醬油小丸子叫有好好吃飯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吃過飯一定會好一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是要我吃什麼啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}馬上就幫你準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳在自作主張地安排什麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吃一口就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}然後我就發誓 再也不干涉你的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只吃一口喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的只吃一口就行了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的 我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}絕對不准食言喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}高城?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的 這裡是他老家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有誰在家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}誰都不在 請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你先去看個電視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}妳想讓我吃什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做好你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.83,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}托您的福 我終於脫離代謝症候群了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.50,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這根本沒脫離啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.21,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不不不 別看我這樣 我的好身材是看不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.42,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}脫光之後可是很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.38,up,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這樣叫好身材的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 做好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令堂留下了食譜的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我擅自拿來看了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只有蛋包飯那一頁 畫了一個很大的花朵記號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我就想 這可能就是你最喜歡的料理也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}小步未在令堂過世後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}靠著這食譜 一直在努力地為你重現這個味道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個...是最後的蛋包飯了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明超甜超難吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這算什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吃太快對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 喝點茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有 請用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吶 友利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我接下來該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再回到學生會 你意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但我已經和妳約好不再互相干涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}蛤? 你在說什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是說吃完這個後就...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你又不只吃一口 而是全部吃完了不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我還邊看著你邊驚訝地想「哇 他超想和我繼續打交道的啊」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真不愧是妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會回學生會的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太好了
Comment: 0,0:22:46.18,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<ED>
